# Native projects are PREBUILD OUTPUT, not source.
# android/ was committed in Jan 2026 and then drifted: it still declared RECORD_AUDIO
# and SYSTEM_ALERT_WINDOW (neither used), pinned versionName 1.0.1 against
# app.config.js's 1.0.3, and - because a committed native project makes EAS skip
# prebuild - silently ignored six months of app.config.js changes. ios/ was never
# committed, so the two platforms were being built from different configuration.
# app.config.js is the single source of truth; let EAS generate these.
